      <title>Arduino系列部分引脚图以及测试代码</title>
      <link href="/posts/23485/"/>
      <url>/posts/23485/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="引脚图"><a href="#引脚图" class="headerlink" title="引脚图"></a>引脚图</h2><h3 id="Arduino-uno"><a href="#Arduino-uno" class="headerlink" title="Arduino-uno"></a>Arduino-uno</h3><p><img src="https://gcore.jsdelivr.net/gh/SempKia/Image/arduino_uno.png" alt="Alt Text"></p><h3 id="Arduino-nano"><a href="#Arduino-nano" class="headerlink" title="Arduino-nano"></a>Arduino-nano</h3><p><img src="https://gcore.jsdelivr.net/gh/SempKia/Image/arduino_nano.png" alt="Alt Text"></p><h3 id="Arduino-mega2560"><a href="#Arduino-mega2560" class="headerlink" title="Arduino-mega2560"></a>Arduino-mega2560</h3><p><img src="https://gcore.jsdelivr.net/gh/SempKia/Image/arduino_mega2560.png" alt="Alt Text"></p><h3 id="Arduino-pro-mini"><a href="#Arduino-pro-mini" class="headerlink" title="Arduino-pro mini"></a>Arduino-pro mini</h3><p><img src="https://gcore.jsdelivr.net/gh/SempKia/Image/arduino_pro_mini.png" alt="Alt Text"></p><h2 id="测试代码"><a href="#测试代码" class="headerlink" title="测试代码"></a>测试代码</h2><h3 id="舵机测试代码"><a href="#舵机测试代码" class="headerlink" title="舵机测试代码"></a>舵机测试代码</h3><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;Servo.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 创建一个名为 servo_9 的 舵机实例 （名称可随你喜欢命名）</span></span><br><span class="line">Servo servo_9;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 初始化程序，在最开始时运行，只运行一次</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title function_">setup</span><span class="params">()</span></span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 使用实例方法 .attach(pin, min, max) 进行配置</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// pin: 舵机所连接的引脚号</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// min: (可选)脉冲宽度（以微秒为单位），对应于舵机上的最小（0度）角度（默认为544）</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// max: (可选)脉冲宽度（以微秒为单位），对应于伺服器上的最大（180度）角度（默认为2400）</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//           (pin, min, max)</span></span><br><span class="line">servo_9.attach(<span class="number">9</span>, <span class="number">500</span>, <span class="number">2500</span>);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 主体程序，不断循环</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title function_">loop</span><span class="params">()</span></span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">while</span> (<span class="number">1</span> == <span class="number">1</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">servo_9.write(<span class="number">0</span>); <span class="comment">// 实例 servo_9 的 舵机 转到0度</span></span><br><span class="line">delay(<span class="number">1000</span>); <span class="comment">// 等待 1000 毫秒</span></span><br><span class="line">servo_9.write(<span class="number">90</span>); <span class="comment">// 实例 servo_9 的 舵机 转到90度</span></span><br><span class="line">delay(<span class="number">1000</span>); <span class="comment">// 等待 1000 毫秒</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="电机测试代码"><a href="#电机测试代码" class="headerlink" title="电机测试代码"></a>电机测试代码</h3><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 定义引脚，此测试代码使用的电机驱动为Tb6612</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">define</span> STBY 6</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">define</span> PWMA 3</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">define</span> AIN1 5</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">define</span> AIN2 4</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 初始化程序，在最开始时运行，只运行一次</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title function_">setup</span><span class="params">()</span> </span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  pinMode(STBY, OUTPUT); <span class="comment">//Tb6612的stable引脚，控制电机正常运作</span></span><br><span class="line">  pinMode(PWMA, OUTPUT); <span class="comment">//Tb6612拥有两个电机的PWM引脚接口，此处只连接了PWMA</span></span><br><span class="line">  pinMode(AIN1, OUTPUT); <span class="comment">//设置A电机的输入1引脚</span></span><br><span class="line">  pinMode(AIN2, OUTPUT); <span class="comment">//设置A电机的输入2引脚</span></span><br><span class="line">  digitalWrite(STBY, HIGH); <span class="comment">//STBY置高电平，启动驱动</span></span><br><span class="line">  analogWrite(PWMA,<span class="number">255</span>); <span class="comment">//255代表启动电机的最大转速</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title function_">loop</span><span class="params">()</span> </span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  digitalWrite(AIN1,HIGH); <span class="comment">//输入1置高电平，2置低电平，电机进行正转</span></span><br><span class="line">  digitalWrite(AIN2,LOW);</span><br><span class="line">  delay(<span class="number">2000</span>); <span class="comment">//延迟2s</span></span><br><span class="line">  digitalWrite(AIN1,LOW); <span class="comment">//取反电位，使电机反转</span></span><br><span class="line">  digitalWrite(AIN2,HIGH);</span><br><span class="line">  delay(<span class="number">2000</span>); <span class="comment">//延迟2s</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
